{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e55b042a36","title":"集结红军准备与胡宗南部作战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b0cd15e99","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":15,"articleId":"e55b042a36"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e2e6f0f411","type":"paragraph","text":"集结红军准备与胡宗南部作战”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36"},{"id":"979f0274a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月15日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36"},{"id":"88f6903b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石仍坚决打红军，与南京妥协一时难成，我们应坚决粉碎其进攻。胡宗南占领豫旺后之行动，两三天后即可明白。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36"},{"id":"e050f81a68","type":"paragraph","text":"目前两三天内，四方面军即在甜水堡、保牛堡集结，二方面军在毛居井及以北集结，一方面军在环县西集结，各兵团鼓动作战准备，胡敌东进时消灭之。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36"},{"id":"18194609f7","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东关于集结红军准备与胡宗南部作战致朱德、张国春、彭德怀、贺龙、任弱时电的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36"}],"page":{"id":"ad25ca5be6","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"e55b042a36","start":297,"end":297}}}},"__N_SSG":true}